== Ayyuren ==
Llan 12 n wayyuren deg teswast tineslemt. Gar-asen 4 n wayyuren d [[ayyur uɣṛis|uɣṛisen]] gan d: [[Raǧeb]], [[Du Lqiɛda]], [[Du Lḥiǧǧa]] d [[Muḥaṛṛam]]

Ayyuren-a ttwassnen s yismawen-nsen iserɣinen (aɛraben) akken i d-ten-yufa Muḥamed ass mi i d-yettwazen. Maca llan ttwassnen s yismawen yemgaraden ɣer iseɣinen  g [[Tazunegzirt taɛrabt|tzunegzirt taserɣint]] send ma ad msegrawen (ad nnejmaɛen) i wakken ad sdukklen ismawen-a send n tuzna n umazun Muḥamed s [[Tasut|tsut]] d wezgen,<ref name="الراشدون - التقويم الهجري">[https://alrashedoon.com/?p=1022 التقويم الهجري]، موقع الراشدون. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017040857/http://alrashedoon.com/?p=1022 |date=17 tuber 2016}}</ref> Yirna ass mi yenfufed usɣan ineslem ɣer iɣerfan niden am [[imaziɣen]] fkan-asen ismawen niden amedya ayyur n Du Lqiɛda ɣer [[Tumẓabt|Yimẓabiyen]] isem-is (Jar n leɛyud).<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://nir-osra.org/%D8%A5%D8%B3%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%85/%D8%A5%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%91%D9%8E%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%92-%D9%86%D9%92-%D8%AA%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A-%D8%B3%D9%92-%D8%AA%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%85%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%8E%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%92|title=ییارن نتزیری ستومڞابت|date=|accessdate=|publisher=|last=|first=|website=|language=Tamaziɣt|trans_title=Ayyuren inselmen s Tumẓabt |akala n ufaylu= https://web.archive.org/web/20190405081422/http://www.nir-osra.org:80/%D8%A5%D8%B3%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%85/%D8%A5%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%91%D9%8E%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%92-%D9%86%D9%92-%D8%AA%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A-%D8%B3%D9%92-%D8%AA%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%85%D9%92%D8%B2%D9%8E%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%92|Azmez n ufaylu=2019-04-05}}</ref>
